<p>The CEO had big visions for our head quarters. He wanted the room to serve as both the MOC and the place to show off our software during demonstrations. The interfaces he envisioned were interactive with gesture recognition in one area, and dark-board type operations overviews across the rest of the screens. </p>
<br>
<br>
<p>I put together ideas to meet these specifications, and rendered a 3D model in Google Sketchup with list of materials to show it was obtainable within budget. </p>
